772
01:00:00,600 --> 01:00:04,400
So who told him that?

773
01:00:04,430 --> 01:00:07,190
It was you, wasn't it, Mr. Son?

774
01:00:08,720 --> 01:00:10,530
What else did you tell him?

775
01:00:10,530 --> 01:00:14,030
I'm sure you told him my name.

776
01:00:14,030 --> 01:00:16,500
Did you also tell him about His Excellency?

777
01:00:25,730 --> 01:00:27,830
 Seoul Central District Prosecutors' Office

778
01:00:27,830 --> 01:00:29,850
 This is going to be an exclusive.

779
01:00:46,220 --> 01:00:48,700
What are you doing?

780
01:00:48,700 --> 01:00:50,790
What about you, what are you doing here?

781
01:00:52,870 --> 01:00:54,990
The van is coming.

782
01:01:06,330 --> 01:01:08,070
Do you feel that you have realized justice?

783
01:01:08,070 --> 01:01:09,800
That people who deserved to die did?

784
01:01:09,800 --> 01:01:12,660
You are now a criminal, can you tell us about that?

785
01:01:12,660 --> 01:01:14,480
Did you really kill those victims?

786
01:01:14,480 --> 01:01:15,480
Didn't they commit suicide?

787
01:01:15,480 --> 01:01:17,730
How did you do it? Please tell us.

788
01:01:17,730 --> 01:01:18,700
Why did you do it?

789
01:01:18,700 --> 01:01:22,750
Your motive wasn't revealed yet, can you tell us now?

790
01:01:34,590 --> 01:01:37,570
If you're going to tell us about the news, you can go, we already know.

791
01:01:37,570 --> 01:01:40,500
Staff Captain Do Jeong Wu submitted a document.

792
01:01:40,500 --> 01:01:42,220
What?

793
01:02:28,830 --> 01:02:29,840
Excuse me.

794
01:02:29,840 --> 01:02:30,770
Team Leader?

795
01:02:30,770 --> 01:02:32,900
I'm a police officer.

796
01:02:35,350 --> 01:02:38,950
Call 119. Hurry!

797
01:02:40,570 --> 01:02:41,620
He is terminally ill.

798
01:02:41,620 --> 01:02:44,890
Cerebral artery dissection can affect him at any time

799
01:02:44,890 --> 01:02:49,870
and once it begins, there is no treatment and even emergency surgery would be

800
01:02:49,870 --> 01:02:52,190
impossible, it says.

801
01:02:55,050 --> 01:02:58,490
 Do you take that without water? What kind of medication is that, anyway?

802
01:02:59,600 --> 01:03:02,470
He's requesting suspension of confinement.

803
01:03:03,810 --> 01:03:07,420
Why? Isn't this just like him?

804
01:03:07,420 --> 01:03:09,990
I guess he'll be going to the hospital now.

805
01:03:32,720 --> 01:03:34,990
Move him here, please.

806
01:03:35,990 --> 01:03:38,050
- I will begin with vital checks.
 - Yes, I understand.

807
01:03:38,050 --> 01:03:39,780
Please bring the equipment quickly.

808
01:03:49,100 --> 01:03:50,500
What will happen to Team Leader?

809
01:03:50,590 --> 01:03:52,990
Come on Gong, say something, Gong!

810
01:04:30,720 --> 01:04:35,760
 White Night Foundation

811
01:05:52,260 --> 01:05:56,470
 I enjoyed riddles since I was young.

812
01:05:56,500 --> 01:06:01,700
 But now merely solving the puzzle isn't enough to satisfy me.

813
01:06:02,400 --> 01:06:07,400
 Because nothing is finished yet.

814
01:06:26,350 --> 01:06:33,330

815
01:06:35,170 --> 01:06:38,160
 Awaken

816
01:06:38,160 --> 01:06:39,630
 Are you really going to die?

817
01:06:39,630 --> 01:06:41,950
 I guess I'm someone who shouldn't live.

818
01:06:41,950 --> 01:06:43,360
 Find it, no matter what.

819
01:06:43,360 --> 01:06:45,430
 Everyone at the station, mobilize now!

820
01:06:45,430 --> 01:06:47,490
 How many people did you receive from the Foundation?

821
01:06:47,490 --> 01:06:49,430
 They are everywhere, and not anywhere.

822
01:06:49,430 --> 01:06:51,430
 So someone came to kill Team Leader?

823
01:06:51,430 --> 01:06:54,420
 Why couldn't he cure his own disease and chose to live the life of a terminally ill patient?

824
01:06:54,420 --> 01:06:57,600
 Do you really want to know who you are?

825
01:06:57,600 --> 01:07:02,650
 I will tell you the whole truth of what happened at White Night Village 28 years ago.

826
01:07:02,650 --> 01:07:05,750
 What? It's not over yet.
